Properties.Name: TableRelation
Properties.Value:
if ("Table Name" = const("Bank Rec.")) "Bank Acc. Reconciliation"."Statement No." where("Bank Account No." = field("Bank Account No."))
            else
            if ("Table Name" = const("Posted Bank Rec.")) "Bank Account Statement"."Statement No." where("Bank Account No." = field("Bank Account No."))
            else
            if ("Table Name" = const("Bank Deposit Header")) "Bank Deposit Header"
            else
            if ("Table Name" = const("Posted Bank Deposit Header")) "Posted Bank Deposit Header"

Properties.Name: TableRelation
Properties.Value: "Gen. Journal Batch".Name where("Journal Template Name" = field("Journal Template Name"))

Properties.Name: CalcFormula
Properties.Value:
exist("Bank Acc. Comment Line" where("Table Name" = const("Bank Deposit Header"),
                                                           "Bank Account No." = field("Bank Account No."),
                                                           "No." = field("No.")))

Properties.Name: CalcFormula
Properties.Value:
- sum("Gen. Journal Line".Amount where("Journal Template Name" = field("Journal Template Name"),
                                                                 "Journal Batch Name" = field("Journal Batch Name")))

Properties.Name: CalcFormula
Properties.Value:
exist("Bank Acc. Comment Line" where("Table Name" = const("Posted Bank Deposit Header"),
                                                           "Bank Account No." = field("Bank Account No."),
                                                           "No." = field("No.")))

Properties.Name: CalcFormula
Properties.Value: sum("Posted Bank Deposit Line".Amount where("Bank Deposit No." = field("No.")))

Properties.Name: Permissions
Properties.Value:
tabledata "Bank Acc. Comment Line" = rd,
                  tabledata "Posted Bank Deposit Line" = r

Properties.Name: TableRelation
Properties.Value:
if ("Account Type" = const("G/L Account")) "G/L Account"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const(Customer)) Customer
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const(Vendor)) Vendor
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const("Bank Account")) "Bank Account"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const("IC Partner")) "IC Partner"

Properties.Name: TableRelation
Properties.Value:
if ("Account Type" = const(Customer)) "Customer Posting Group"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const(Vendor)) "Vendor Posting Group"

Properties.Name: TableRelation
Properties.Value:
if ("Account Type" = const("G/L Account")) "G/L Entry"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const(Customer)) "Cust. Ledger Entry"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const(Vendor)) "Vendor Ledger Entry"
            else
            if ("Account Type" = const("Bank Account")) "Bank Account Ledger Entry"
